  <div id="text-content_2E1AEEC0-1E1C-0135-BF8C-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have a question or comment about an announcement, you can reply directly to that announcement.</p>
<p>You can reply in both course and group announcements. This lesson shows how to reply in a course, but the steps are the same.</p>
<p>If the steps in this lesson do not match what is displayed in your course, learn how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-reply-to-an-announcement-in-Announcements-Redesign-as/ta-p/478620" target="_blank">reply to an announcement in the Announcements Redesign interface</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>Not all announcements may allow replies. Additionally, <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-allow-or-disallow-announcement-replies-in-a-course/ta-p/707" target="_blank">announcement replies</a> may be disabled in Course Settings or at the account level.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_announcements" data-step-uuid="9EB5D2FE-A655-4CC9-9029-309DD47B3817">
    <h2 id="open_announcements" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcements</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/740/449/original/3c5068ac-0c9f-40e5-81fd-5d6793cbe474.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcements" height="267" width="179">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2E1B2380-1E1C-0135-BF8E-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Announcements</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_the_announcement" data-step-uuid="9A6355E7-DF83-4CAB-88DB-456847573872">
