  <div id="text-content_2E1B9150-1E1C-0135-BF92-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Reply</strong> box.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="post_reply" data-step-uuid="43A840DE-875E-4F41-96E1-CAC6E30C0B43">
    <h2 id="post_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Post Reply</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/036/856/original/ee75bbcb-5d5c-4e9a-92c7-e93e576f3383.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/036/856/medium/ee75bbcb-5d5c-4e9a-92c7-e93e576f3383.png" srcset="" alt="Post Reply" height="482" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2E1BC6C0-1E1C-0135-BF94-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Format your response and add media, links, photos, and/or equations using the Rich Content Editor [1]. Click the <strong>Post Reply </strong>button [2].</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> The Rich Content Editor includes a word count display below the bottom right corner of the text box.</p>
